            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/b6acdc4b276bccb8/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-b6acdc4b276bccb8-f09fcd twpub-b6acdc4b276bccb8-6b4cd0\"><p>For additional contact information:<br>\n\nÂ Â Â Â Â Dr. Gregory B. Newby<br>\n\nÂ Â Â Â Â Chief Executive and Director<br>\n\nÂ Â Â Â Â gbnewby@pglaf.org<br>\n</p></div>"
        },
